&lt;p&gt;Preparing the family tree using the following symbols:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/20/11/sym_BR.PNG&quot; style=&quot;width: 211px; height: 287px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

